| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1633 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c9a1a291-bfb6-5eb3-94ec-2d6149351bd6"
